msgstr ":ref:`Estudiantes <learn>` - empezar aquí"

#: ../../index.rst:59
msgid "Weather you are using Kolibri at your school, in a training center or at home, learn how to :ref:`open <access_learner>` it on your device, what kind of :ref:`content and activities <content_types>` can you work with, and how to submit :ref:`exams <exams>` created by your coaches or tutors."
msgstr "Independientemente si usas Kolibri en tu escuela, centro de formación o a casa, aquí puedes aprender como :ref:`abrirlo <access_learner>` en tu ordenador, que tipo de :ref:`contenido y actividades <content_types>` puedes hacer, y como entregar :ref:`exámenes <exams>` preparados por tus tutores o profesores."

#: ../../index.rst:65
msgid "For :ref:`Coaches and Tutors <coach>`"
msgstr "Para :ref:`tutores y educadores <coach>`"

#: ../../index.rst:67
msgid "Read how to :ref:`monitor activity <recent_view>` and :ref:`track the progress <track_progress>` of your learners on whole topics and exercises, all the way to single answer to a particular questions. Create and :ref:`manage different learner groups <manage_groups>`, administer :ref:`exams <manage_exams>` and view reports."
msgstr "Familiarízate como :ref:`monitorizar la actividad <recent_view>` y :ref:`hacer el seguimiento del progreso <track_progress>` de tus estudiantes por temas y ejercicios, hasta revisar las respuestas a particulares respuestas. Crea y :ref:`gestiona grupos de estudiantes <manage_groups>`, administra :ref:`exámenes <manage_exams>` y visualiza informes."

#: ../../index.rst:73
msgid "For :ref:`Administrators and Superusers <manage>` of Kolibri"
msgstr "Para :ref:`administradores y superusuarios <manage>` de Kolibri"

#: ../../index.rst:75
msgid "Begin by reading how to :ref:`install <install>` and :ref:`start <access>` Kolibri server on the supported platforms, and :ref:`configure other devices <access_LAN>` in the local network to access its content. Proceed on how to :ref:`import content channels <manage_content_ref>`, create and manage :ref:`users <manage_users_ref>` and :ref:`classes <manage_classes_ref>`. Configure the :ref:`settings for your facility <manage_facility_ref>`, and assign or edit :ref:`permissions <permissions>` for other users. Learn how to work with Kolibri from :ref:`the command line <command_line>`, :ref:`troubleshoot network issues <network>`, and ask for support on our :ref:`Community Forums <support>`."
msgstr "Empieza por leer como :ref:`instalar <install>` y :ref:`acceder <access>` el servidor de Kolibri en plataformas soportadas, y :ref:`configura otros dispositivos <access_LAN>` en la red local para acceder su contenido. Continua leyendo como :ref:`importar canales de contenido <manage_content_ref>`, crear y gestionar :ref:`usuarios <manage_users_ref>` y :ref:`clases <manage_classes_ref>`. Configura los :ref:`ajustes de tu centro educativo <manage_facility_ref>`, y asigna o edita :ref:`permisos <permissions>` para otros usuarios. Aprende como trabajar con Kolibri desde :ref:`la línea de comando <command_line>`, :ref:`resuelve problemas de red <network>`, y contactar soporte en nuestros :ref:`foros de comunidad <support>`."

